# LockBit Ransomware Campaign Overview

## Ransomware Family

LockBit 3.0

## Type

Ransomware-as-a-Service (RaaS)

## First Observed

2019

## Target Industries

* Healthcare
* Finance
* Government
* Manufacturing
* Technology

## Initial Access Methods

* Phishing emails
* Exploited vulnerabilities
* Compromised VPN accounts
* RDP brute force attacks

## Key Characteristics

* Fast encryption speed
* Double extortion (data theft + encryption)
* Automated lateral movement
* Data exfiltration before encryption

## Encryption Methods

LockBit typically uses:

* AES encryption
* RSA encryption

Encrypted files often include the extension:

.lockbit
